<div class="code">
Chief Agent<br>
Workflow Engine<br>
State Machine<br>
Task Center<br>
Agent Center<br>
Knowledge Center<br>
Memory Center<br>
Test Center<br>
Documentation Center
</div>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Architecture Diagram</h2>
<pre>
Human
  │
  ▼

Chief Agent
(唯一调度中心)

  │
  ▼

Planning Layer
├─ Requirement Task
├─ BA Task
├─ Architect Task
├─ Security Task
└─ Test Design Task

  │
  ▼

Development Manager

├─ DB Task
├─ Backend Task
├─ API Task
├─ Frontend Task
├─ Unit Test Task
└─ DevOps Task

  │
  ▼

Verification Layer

├─ Code Review Task
├─ Integration Test Task
├─ E2E Test Task
├─ Performance Test Task
└─ Security Test Task

  │
  ▼

Bug Loop

Root Cause Task
      ↓
Fix Task
      ↓
Regression Task
      ↓
PASS ?
 ├─ NO → Root Cause
 └─ YES

  │
  ▼

Documentation Layer

├─ Requirement Update
├─ Design Update
├─ API Update
└─ Changelog Update

  │
  ▼

Retrospective Layer

├─ Lessons Learned
├─ Best Practice Update
├─ Prompt Update
└─ Knowledge Update

  │
  ▼

DONE
</pre>
</section>

<section>
<h2>State Machine</h2>
<pre>
NEW
ANALYSIS
DESIGN
DEVELOPMENT
REVIEW
TEST
FIX
DOC
RETRO
DONE
</pre>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Task Definition</h2>
<pre>
{
  "id":"task-id",
  "type":"backend",
  "state":"running",
  "input":{},
  "output":{},
  "owner":"agent-name",
  "retry":0
}
</pre>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Agent Rules</h2>
<pre>
1. 每个Agent必须独立Task运行
2. 每个Agent独立上下文
3. 每个Agent独立Memory
4. Agent之间禁止直接调用
5. 必须通过Chief Agent调度
6. 所有结果写入Task Center
</pre>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Knowledge System</h2>
<pre>
knowledge/

├─ architecture/
├─ bugs/
├─ best-practices/
├─ retrospectives/
├─ prompts/
└─ domain-rules/
</pre>
</section>

